5. **ivosidenib 2018 → 2023 MDS expansion + olutasidenib 2024 MDS research** = IDH1 R132H paradigm MDS 확장. AML-only 시대 종료. quantum-VQE 의 IDH1 selectivity ivosidenib vs olutasidenib comparator.
6. **venetoclax + azacitidine HR-MDS research** = cross-aml_specific spillover. AML 1L (2018+) 후 HR-MDS Phase 3 research. BCL-2 + DNMT1 dual mechanism.
7. **magrolimab Phase 3 fail 2023** = anti-CD47 paradigm 좌절. HR-MDS 1L 좌절 → "do not eat me" CD47-SIRPα checkpoint heme malig 임상 의의 재평가. cross-cancer + immuno-oncology.
8. **erythropoietin + darbepoetin alfa 1989-2001** = historical EPO-responsive LR-MDS supportive paradigm. luspatercept (2019) 이전 표준 + 만성. cross-hematology + nephrology.
9. **allogeneic HSCT** = HR-MDS + AML transformation 만성 cure 유일. RIC vs MAC + GvHD + GvL. cross-bone_marrow_failure + transplant + hsct_gvhd_specific.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, MDS 임상 의미 한정.

